<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<PXML xmlns="http://openpandora.org/namespaces/PXML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="PXML_schema.xsd">
  <package id="package.pandafe">
    <titles>
      <title lang="en_US">Pandafe</title>
    </titles>
    <descriptions>
      <description lang="en_US">Pandafe is a sort of "universal" SDL frontend for Pandora games and emulators.

It was written especially for the Pandora, with the following goals:
* browse and run all roms and games from a single program
* specify commandline options for each game via a menu
* be fully configurable and extendable via the program itself
* use only dpad and buttons to do all this (no touching, heh)
* persist data via yaml, for human reading/writing/sharing
</description>
    </descriptions>
    <version major="@PACKAGE_VERSION_MAJOR@" minor="@PACKAGE_VERSION_MINOR@" release="@PACKAGE_VERSION_RELEASE@" build="@PACKAGE_VERSION_BUILD@"/>
    <author name="nuhrin" email="nuhrin@oceanic.to"/>
  </package>

